The original data is taken from Knowledge, networks and nations -Â Global scientific collaboration in the 21st century, Royal Society (2011) (<a href="http://royalsociety.org/uploadedFiles/Royal_Society_Content/Influencing_Policy/Reports/2011-03-28-Knowledge-networks-nations.pdf">online here</a>).[/ref]


